data.text:
@LouHaigh I'd love a 4 day work week as a rule, because she's absolutely right that it DOES make people more productive, more healthy, and more happy.

Unfortunately that "news" is complete bunk. Finland isn't introducing a 4 day workweek or a 6h workday. We're just working towards that
